WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.533 --> 00:00:04.966
What exactly do you want?

2
00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:07.533
A murderer like you

3
00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.366
How could you be released so early?

4
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.166
Wasn’t your sentence supposed to end in a year?

5
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:14.100
My sentence was reduced

6
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:17.133
Reduced?

7
00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:24.266
My daughter’s bones aren’t even cold yet

8
00:00:25.066 --> 00:00:26.533
What gives you the right to get a sentence reduction?

9
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:29.266
Someone like you

10
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:31.500
Should have spent your life behind bars

11
00:00:32.133 --> 00:00:32.933
Shen Yu

12
00:00:34.333 --> 00:00:35.633
I’m also a mother

13
00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:37.533
I also have a child

14
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:39.533
It’s been six years

15
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.333
You miss your daughter

16
00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:43.533
Do you think I don’t miss my son?

17
00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:48.366
I just wanted to be released

18
00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:49.300
and reunite with my son

19
00:00:49.333 --> 00:00:50.833
Is that wrong?

20
00:00:52.766 --> 00:00:53.700
Reunite?

21
00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:56.766
Reunite, you say?

22
00:01:05.466 --> 00:01:06.266
Then tell me...

23
00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.500
Where can I go to reunite with my daughter!?

24
00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:12.766
In heaven, maybe?

25
00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:20.066
What if Shen Yu knew

26
00:01:20.533 --> 00:01:22.100
her daughter was murdered

27
00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:24.500
Could she bear it?

28
00:01:27.066 --> 00:01:28.300
Ye Ci, you know what?

29
00:01:30.700 --> 00:01:32.633
My daughter’s name was Jiang Tai

30
00:01:35.133 --> 00:01:36.566
But because of you

31
00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:39.133
Her future was stolen from her
(*) Her name and the word 'future' are homophones in Chinese

32
00:01:47.133 --> 00:01:49.733
I’m so sorry, so sorry

33
00:01:49.966 --> 00:01:50.633
I’m sorry

34
00:01:51.133 --> 00:01:52.566
She no longer had a future

35
00:01:53.466 --> 00:01:55.133
I'm truly sorry, truly sorry